<br>
Anyway...I'm looking for a place to quad or solo at 47th. I am on a PvP server so some of the places you recommend may not be available to me. Currently I'm still soloing giants in GD, though tonight a druid and I are going to attempt to quad kite some in EW.<br>
<br>
Recommendations? ideas for 47 AND 48 would be appreciated. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=genadiel>Genadiel</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/30/01 12:18:54 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Happ</span><hr size=1> I was barely into 47 yesterday and managed to hit 48 just camping Happ in Lower Fay, right by the Steamfont zone.  Good exp with 5 minute respawn.  No wandering mobs to harass you.  You'd like it.<br>
<br>
